3921	  M_f\) as the localization of \(M\) at the powers of \(f\): it carries an
3922	  \(\operatorname{IsLocalizedModule}(\operatorname{powers} f)\) instance. Moreover the global component
3923	  \(\operatorname{toOpen}(M, \top)\) is an isomorphism (Mathlib's
